<table width="auto"  border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0"><tr><td colspan=3>House Bill/Resolution NO. <b>HB00528</b></td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>FULL TITLE : AN ACT AMENDING BATAS PAMBANSA BLG. 68 OR THE CORPORATION CODE OF THE PHILIPPINES</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>ABSTRACT : Allows corporations perpetual existence, removes minimum number of incorporators and allows one person corporations; aims to improve ease of doing business by allowing electronic submission and on-line registration the stockholders and deters abuses, fraud and graft; provides solutions to the problem of perpetual holdovers; and, fortifies the regulatory powers of the Commission.</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>PRINCIPAL AUTHOR/S : <b>BATOCABE, RODEL M., GARBIN, ALFREDO JR. A., CO, CHRISTOPHER S.</b></td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>DATE FILED : 2016-06-30</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>SIGNIFICANCE: NATIONAL</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>NATURE : Economic</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>CO-AUTHORS (Journal Entries) :</td></tr><tr><td>1. Salceda (008 2016-08-09)</td><td>2. Uybarreta (023 2017-09-12)</td><tr><td>3. Olivarez (000 2017-09-28)</td><tr><td colspan=3><b>ACTIONS TAKEN BY THE COMMITTEE</b></td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>COMMITEE HEARINGS/ACTIONS:</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3><b>&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp1. Referred to Stakeholders on 2016-09-19</b><tr><td colspan=3><b>&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp2. Deliberated upon by the Mother Committee on 2017-09-25</b><tr><td colspan=3>&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp-For submission of position papers by stakeholders</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3><b>&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp3. Deliberated by the TWG on 2018-02-13</b><tr><td colspan=3><b>&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp4. Deliberated by the TWG on 2018-02-20</b><tr><td colspan=3><b>&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp5. Deliberated by the TWG on 2018-03-15</b><tr><td colspan=3><b>&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp6. Deliberated by the TWG on 2018-05-17</b><tr><td colspan=3><b>&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp7. 